{"title":"罪魁祸首","authors":["易和元　韦启美"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":4,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"罪魁祸首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"易和元诗　韦启美画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一手拿橄榄枝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一手拿弓箭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涂脂抹粉巧装扮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“和平”“自由”挂嘴边："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是古巴内政，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与咱美国不相干！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们吃的美国饭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用的美国钱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从美国基地去轰炸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接受咱美国训练，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一切一切，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们完全有“自由”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱只从背后指点！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说得再香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说得再甜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"染血的双手藏不住，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狰狞嘴脸难遮掩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古巴人民爱自由，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿着砍刀拿着枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要为保卫祖国而战！（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}